---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About & Hire Me" description="About mmmaxwwwell — software engineer available for contract and freelance work.">
  <main class="flex-1 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-6 sm:py-12 w-full">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-3">About</h1>
    <div class="h-1 w-16 sm:w-24 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--accent-pink)] via-[var(--accent-purple)] to-[var(--accent-cyan)] mb-6 sm:mb-8"></div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>Software engineer riding the AI wave. I build things with code, solder, and filament.</p>
      <p>This blog is where I write about my projects: software development, hobbyist electronics, 3D printing and OpenSCAD modeling.</p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mt-10 sm:mt-14 mb-3">Hire Me</h2>
    <div class="h-1 w-16 sm:w-24 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--accent-cyan)] via-[var(--accent-purple)] to-[var(--accent-pink)] mb-6 sm:mb-8"></div>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>I'm a full-time software engineer, but I take on contract and freelance work when there's no conflict of interest. I'm strongest in full-stack development, but I also do embedded systems, hardware prototyping, and 3D modeling.</p>
      <p>If you've got a side project that needs building, reach out.</p>
    </div>

    
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
